<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ja">

<head>
  <meta charset="utf-8">
  <title>返却</title>
  <link href="https://stackpath.bootstrapcdn.com/bootstrap/4.5.2/css/bootstrap.min.css" rel="stylesheet">
</head>

<body>
  <header class="container mt-3 mb-3">
    <h1>物品貸出登録 プロトタイプ</h1>
    <h3>2025年度版</h3>
  </header>
  <main class="container">
    <h2>返却確認</h2>
    <h3>以下の物品を返却処理します。よろしいですか？</h3>
    <div class="return-item border p-3 mb-3">
      <div class="list-item-id mb-2">ID: <%= data.id %></div>
      <div class="list-item-name mb-2">物品名: <%= data.item_name %></div>
      <div class="list-item-piece mb-2">個数: <%= data.item_piece %>個</div>
      <div class="list-item-class mb-2">クラス: <%= data.class_name %></div>
      <div class="list-item-date mb-2">貸出日時: <%= data.lent_time %></div>
      <div class="list-item-button d-flex justify-content-between">
        <form action="/return/<%= data.id %>" method="post" class="mr-2">
          <button type="submit" class="btn btn-primary">返却</button>
        </form>
        <form action="/list" method="get">
          <button type="submit" class="btn btn-secondary">キャンセル</button>
        </form>
      </div>
    </div>
  </main>
  <script src="https://code.jquery.com/jquery-3.5.1.slim.min.js"></script>
  <script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/@popperjs/core@2.5.4/dist/umd/popper.min.js"></script>
  <script src="https://stackpath.bootstrapcdn.com/bootstrap/4.5.2/js/bootstrap.min.js"></script>
</body>

</html>
